# Logs Directory

This directory is reserved for application log files.

## Purpose
- Application runtime logs
- Error logs
- Access logs
- Debug information

## Log Files
- `datalab.log` - Main application log
- `access.log` - HTTP access log
- `error.log` - Error-specific log

## Note
This directory is ignored by Git (except for this `.gitkeep` file) to prevent committing log data.
Logs may contain sensitive information and should not be version controlled.
